\p
\v 21 вҖҳ\add вүҲAnyoneВҰ94772\add* who has sex with an animalВҰ94777 will be cursedВҰ94771.вҖҷ
\p Then the peopleВҰ94781 must reply, вҖҳLet it be so.вҖҷ
\p
\v 22 вҖҳ\add вүҲAny maleВҰ94786\add* who sleeps with his sister \add вүҲor his half sister\add* will be cursedВҰ94785.вҖҷ
\p Then the peopleВҰ94800 must reply, вҖҳLet it be so.вҖҷ
